=\"\"><span class=\"c4\">曾任蔡英文辦公室“少數民族轉型正義委員會”委員</span></li></ul></td><td class=\"w-16\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\"><span class=\"c4\">額手稱慶</span></li><li class=\"\"><span class=\"c4\">台獨亂說話，上天收了她</span></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>",
